#
# To create python bindings for libecbufr
# You need to have  cython installed.
# Then you can use either python or python3 as follows :
#
# Create python 3 bindings
#
#     python3 setup.py build_ext -i
#
#
# Create python 2 bindings
#
#     python setup.py build_ext -i
#
# Then copy the content of  "ecbufr" directory to a location and have that 
# location added to PYTHONPATH 
#
# If libecbufr is created with shared enabled. You may also need to add the 
# location of libecbufr.so to LD_LIBRARY_PATH
#
